1.0.name: wordpress/degaa-analytics
1.0.description:
** This plugin requires an active account with Degaa Analytics (FREE). Create your free site profile at http://www.degaa.net/signup to receive your tracking key and to access your online stats.

Degaa Analytics Wordpress plugin allows for code-less integration into your Wordpress website or blog giving real-time, individual visitor tracking and traffic analysis.

Plug-in Features:

  • Automatically include Degaa tracking code onto each page
  • Ignore Administrators from tracking
  • Enable/Disable tracking of Admin pages

Degaa Features:

  • Real-time visitor feed
  • Accurate Click-stream data
  • Traffic Analysis and Summary
  • Real-time map overlay and location data
  • Individual user profiles and loyalty tracking
  • Search engine optimization tracking
